Package: perturbKit
Title: Package for the management, loading, and analysis of perturbational biological datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ian", "Smith", email="ianc.smith@mail.utoronto.ca", role=c("aut"), comment=c(ORCID="")),
    person("Benjamin", "Haibe-Kains", email="benjamin.haibe.kains@utoronto.ca", role=c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: This package is designed for analysis on perturbational data in the Benjamin Haibe-Kains lab. It contains
    a set of functions for computing similarities between perturbational signatures from the L1000 project, 
    originally generated as part of the NIH LINCS Consortium. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
